data.description: Beautiful 1 story home features 4 bedrooms and 3 full baths.  The 4th bedroom has a en suite bathroom.  Plenty of space in every single room!  Also includes a study, formal dining, spacious laundry room that will accommodate your freezer as well as the washer and dryer.   Nicely appointed island kitchen with stainless appliances, 5 burner gas cooktop, granite counters, tile backsplash and 42" cabinets  and large pantry that offers plenty of storage.  A few extras such as recently installed solar panels, tankless water heater, covered patio, full sprinkler system, epoxy sealed flooring in the 3 car oversized garage.  Come and enjoy the convenience of entertainment, shopping and business.  Fosters Ridge offers a Community Center, swimming pools, walking trails and playgroud.  Buyer to assume Solar Payment of $105.00 a month.
